2:T704,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Drift better than Forethought?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Drift scores 7.0 overall while Forethought scores 7.0. Drift is best for B2B sales teams and demand generation, while Forethought excels for mid-market support and SaaS companies."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Drift or Forethought?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Drift starts at Custom and Forethought starts at Custom.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Drift to Forethought?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Drift and Forethought support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Drift vs Forethought?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Drift holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10. Forethought has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Drift for excellent for b2b lead qualification and Forethought for strong ticket categorization and routing."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Drift or Forethought?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Forethought for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Drift remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize excellent for b2b lead qualification. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"com